title: Ep. 1147 - Jetha Being Accused - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide blames for the trucks being parked in society. Daya suspects Sunderlal. Sunderlal denies allegations against him. Jetha and Bhide find someone lying below the truck.

title: Ep. 1148 - The Mystery Man - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Jetha find out that the man lying below the truck does not belong to the society and is sleeping. Suspecting him to be the truck driver, they try to wake him up.

title: Ep. 1149 - Champaklal Goes Insane - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone asks Jetha to call Natu and Baga to confirm if the trucks belong to them. They deny getting any trucks parked in Gokuldham Society

title: Ep. 1150 - Bollywood's Muscle Man In Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya checks the second truck only to find cartons of apples. Jetha cracks the riddle and tells everyone that superstar Dharmendra is the one who has sent the truck full of goods for them. Finally, the truck is unloaded.

title: Ep. 1151 - Dharam Garam Interacts - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dharmendra interacts with everyone and praises them.

title: Ep. 1152 - The Mystery Unfolds - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: They discuss the trucks that had come to deliver the goods. Gokuldham society praises Dharmendra for his work and contribution to Bollywood. Police tell he has to arrest Jetha for creating all the confusion.

title: Ep. 1153 - Mr. And Mrs. Sodhi Surprised - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Mr. and Mrs. Sodhi are back. Daya asks them to have lunch and then leave for their home. The Sodhis are surprised to see that the house is cleaned and decorated by all the ladies of Gokuldham. Tapu Sena is worried about the result.

title: Ep. 1154 - Dreams And Imagination - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the parents dream about their kids achieving their goals. Daya panics and asks Jetha to go out as she feels there could be an earthquake. Besides results, Jetha is worried about Tapu's aim in life.

title: Ep. 1155 - Taarak Counsels Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak explains Jetha as how it is important to take results lightly and scolding kids is not the solution

title: Ep. 1156 - Daya Interrupts Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is about to leave for his shop, meets Babita in the compound. Daya calls out to Jetha from the balcony to which Jetha becomes furious.

title: Ep. 1157 - Daya Scares Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal wishes all the kids the very best so that they get good marks. He is about to step down when Daya stops him saying a cat has just crossed that path and that he should not be taking steps forward.

title: Ep. 1158 - Bhide Is All Praises - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone thanks Bhide for being a good teacher. Popatlal asks Bhide if he has given more attention to Sonu.

title: Ep. 1159 - The Coaching Scam - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal reaches a coaching institute where he finds Sonu's photo.

title: Ep. 1160 - Jetha Is Furious With Bhide - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha thinks Bhide has lied to him. Jetha decides to inform everyone about this at the party. He thinks of sharing this with Taarak first but waits for the right moment.

title: Ep. 1161 - Jethalal Is Upset - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is still upset with Bhide and has dressed differently. Taarak addresses Bhide and family and praises them. Tapu Sena offers a song to him. Daya asks Jetha if he is upset.
